const initialState={
    fullName: 'fd',
    preferredName: [],
    birthDate: [],
    gender: [],
    maritalStatus: [],
    currentStreet1: [],
    currentStreet2: [],
    currentCity: [],
    currentState: [],
    currentCountry: [],
    currentAddressProof: [],
    permanentStreet1: [],
    permanentStreet2: [],
    permanentCity: [],
    permanentState: [],
    permanentCountry: [],
    permanentAddressProof: [],
    emergencyName1: [],
    emergencyMobile1: [],
    emergencyRelationship1: [],
    emergencyName2: [],
    emergencyMobile2: [],
    emergencyRelationship2: [],
    jobHireDate: [],
    jobSalary: [],
    jobCurrentSalary: [],
    jobBond: [],
    idProof: [],
    picture: [],
    feedback: []
}
const EmployeeReducer=(state=initialState,action)=>{
    switch(action.type){
        case "SHOW_EMPLOYEE":
            return state
        case "ADD_EMPLOYEE":
            {action.payload}
            
            default:
                return state
    }
}
export default EmployeeReducer
